            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3>Promocja:</h3>
            <img src="~/Content/Images/pizzaSlide_1.jpg" style="width: 100%; height: 200px;" />
            <p>
                Praesent in placerat risus, et ornare lectus. Praesent turpis tortor, consectetur quis enim id, consequat pharetra velit. Nullam tempor convallis ante at finibus.
